アニオンギャップ4
CDISC Definition-J
生物学的標本中の測定されていない陰イオンの計算された推定値（血清ナトリウム + 血清カリウムの合計と血清重炭酸塩 + 塩化物の合計の差として計算されます）。
NCI Preferred Term-J
アニオンギャップ4測定

APRI
xxTEST
AST to Platelet Ratio Index
CDISC Synonym(s)
APRI Score; AST to Platelet Ratio Index
CDISC Definition
A calculation that indicates the likely presence of liver cirrhosis and fibrosis, measured as the relative measurement of aspartate aminotransferase (AST) to AST upper limit of normal, divided by the platelet count, and multiplied by 100.
NCI Preferred Term
Aspartate Aminotransferase to Platelet Ratio Index
xxTEST-J
AST対血小板比指数
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
APRIスコア；AST対血小板比指数
CDISC Definition-J
肝硬変および線維症が存在する可能性を示す計算。AST の正常上限値に対するアスパラギン酸アミノトランスフェラーゼ (AST) の相対測定値として測定され、血小板数で割り、100 を掛けます。
NCI Preferred Term-J
アスパラギン酸アミノトランスフェラーゼ対血小板比指数

Activated Partial Thromboplastin Time
CDISC Synonym(s)
Activated Partial Thromboplastin Time
CDISC Definition
A measurement of the length of time that it takes for clotting to occur when activating reagents are added to a biological specimen. The test is partial due to the absence of tissue factor (Factor III) from the reaction mixture.
NCI Preferred Term
Activated Partial Thromboplastin Time
xxTEST-J
活性化部分トロンボプラスチン時間
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
活性化部分トロンボプラスチン時間
CDISC Definition-J
活性化試薬を生体試料に加え、凝固が起こるまでの時間を測定する検査です。反応混合物に組織因子（第III因子）が含まれていないため、この検査は部分的なものです。
NCI Preferred Term-J
活性化部分トロンボプラスチン時間

xxTESTCD
BLYMXM
xxTEST
B-lymphocyte Crossmatch
CDISC Synonym(s)
B-lymphocyte Crossmatch
CDISC Definition
A measurement to determine human leukocyte antigens (HLA) histocompatibility between the recipient and the donor by examining the presence or absence of the recipient's anti-HLA antibody reactivity towards HLA antigens expressed on the donor B-lymphocytes
NCI Preferred Term
B-lymphocyte Crossmatch Measurement
xxTEST-J
Bリンパ球交差適合試験
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
Bリンパ球交差適合試験
CDISC Definition-J
ドナーBリンパ球に発現しているヒト白血球抗原（HLA）に対するレシピエントの抗HLA抗体反応の有無を調べることによって、レシピエントとドナー間のHLA組織適合性を決定する測定
NCI Preferred Term-J
Bリンパ球交差適合試験

定義された期間（例：1 時間）にわたって生物学的標本中に排出されるケモカイン（C-C モチーフ）リガンド 2 の量を測定します。
NCI Preferred Term-J
ケモカイン（C-Cモチーフ）リガンド2排泄率

A calculation that indicates the likely presence of fatty liver disease, taking into account waist circumference, body mass index, triglyceride concentrations, and gamma-glutamyltransferase activity. (Bedogni G, Bellentani S, Miglioli L, Masutti F, Passal
NCI Preferred Term
Fatty Liver Index

CDISC Synonym(s)
Interpretation
CDISC Definition
An act or process of elucidation; explication, or explanation of the meaning of the event or thing via the assignment of objects from the domain to the constants of a formal language, truth-values to the proposition symbols, truth-functions to the connect
NCI Preferred Term
Interpretation
xxTEST-J
解釈
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
解釈
CDISC Definition-J
解明の行為またはプロセス。ドメインのオブジェクトを形式言語の定数に、真理値を命題記号に、真理関数を接続に割り当てることによって、イベントまたは事物の意味を説明する。
NCI Preferred Term-J
解釈

JTAG
xxTEST
JT Interval, Aggregate
CDISC Synonym(s)
JT Interval, Aggregate
CDISC Definition
An aggregate JT value based on the measurement of JT intervals from multiple beats within a single ECG. The method of aggregation, which can vary, is typically a measure of central tendency such as the mean.
NCI Preferred Term
Aggregate JT Interval
xxTEST-J
JT間隔、集計
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
JT間隔、集計
CDISC Definition-J
1回の心電図における複数の心拍のJT間隔の測定に基づく集計JT値。集計方法は様々ですが、通常は平均値などの中心傾向の尺度が用いられます。
NCI Preferred Term-J
集計JT間隔

A JT single beat interval that is corrected for heart rate using Bazett's formula, based on a QT interval measured on a single beat utilizing one or more ECG leads.
NCI Preferred Term
Single Beat JTCB Interval
xxTEST-J

Summary (Max) JT Interval
CDISC Synonym(s)
Summary (Max) JT Interval
CDISC Definition
The maximum duration (time) of the JT interval, obtained from a set of measurements of the JT interval. The JT interval is defined as the time from the J point (end of ventricular depolarization, the point at which the QRS meets the ST segment) to the end
NCI Preferred Term
Maximum JT Duration
xxTEST-J

J-Tpeak Interval, Aggregate
CDISC Definition
An aggregate J-Tpeak value based on the measurement of J-Tpeak intervals from multiple beats within a single ECG. The method of aggregation, which can vary, is typically a measure of central tendency such as the mean.

LCI to 2.5% Initial Concentration
CDISC Synonym(s)
LCI to 1/40th Initial Concentration; LCI to 2.5% Initial Concentration; Lung Clearance Index to 1/40th Initial Concentration; Lung Clearance Index to 2.5% Initial Concentration
CDISC Definition
A representative measurement of the number of times the volume of air in the lung at the start of the washout (the Functional Residual Capacity) must be recycled to decrease the tracer to 2.5% (or 1/40th) of its initial concentration.
NCI Preferred Term
Lung Clearance Index to 2.5% Initial Concentration
xxTEST-J
LCIから2.5%の初期濃度まで

CDISC Definition-J
洗浄開始時の肺の空気量（機能的残留気量）をリサイクルしてトレーサーを初期濃度の 2.5%（または 40 分の 1）まで下げる必要がある回数を表す代表的な測定値。
NCI Preferred Term-J
初期濃度2.5%までの肺クリアランス指数

The (current sum of volumes minus the lowest sum of volumes previously recorded) divided by the lowest sum of volumes previously recorded, multiplied by 100.
NCI Preferred Term

PR Segment, Aggregate
CDISC Definition

QRS_AXIS
xxTEST
QRS Axis
CDISC Synonym(s)
QRS Axis
CDISC Definition
A numerical representation of the electrocardiographic vector assessed at maximum deviation of the QRS complex from the isoelectric baseline, usually reported for the frontal plane.
NCI Preferred Term
QRS Axis
xxTEST-J
QRS軸
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
QRS軸
CDISC Definition-J
等電位ベースラインからの QRS 複合体の最大偏差で評価された心電図ベクトルの数値表現。通常は前頭部面で報告されます。
NCI Preferred Term-J
QRS軸

xxTESTCD
QRSAG
xxTEST
QRS Duration, Aggregate
CDISC Synonym(s)
QRS Duration, Aggregate
CDISC Definition
An aggregate QRS value based on the measurement of QRS intervals from multiple beats within a single ECG. The method of aggregation, which can vary, is typically a measure of central tendency such as the mean.
NCI Preferred Term
Aggregate QRS Duration
xxTEST-J

CDISC Synonym(s)-J
QRS持続時間、合計
CDISC Definition-J

NCI Preferred Term-J

Total Respiratory System Resistance
CDISC Synonym(s)
Total Respiratory System Resistance
CDISC Definition
A calculated value based on all factors that influence the flow of gas from the airway opening to the alveoli, including airway resistance, and tissue resistance of the lung and chest wall. (NCI)
NCI Preferred Term
Total Respiratory System Resistance
xxTEST-J
全呼吸器系抵抗
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
全呼吸器系抵抗
CDISC Definition-J
気道抵抗、肺と胸壁の組織抵抗など、気道開口部から肺胞へのガスの流れに影響を与えるすべての要因に基づいて計算された値。(NCI)
NCI Preferred Term-J
全呼吸器系抵抗

RRSM
xxTEST
RR Interval, Single Measurement
CDISC Synonym(s)
RR Interval, Single Measurement
CDISC Definition
An electrocardiographic measurement of the interval between two consecutive R waves. If R waves are not present, this measurement may utilize the interval between the most easily identified components of the QRS complex within two consecutive beats.
NCI Preferred Term
RR Interval Single Measurement
xxTEST-J
RR間隔、単一測定
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
RR間隔、単一測定
CDISC Definition-J
連続する2つのR波間の間隔を測定する心電図検査。R波が存在しない場合は、連続する2つの心拍におけるQRS波群の最も識別しやすい成分間の間隔を測定することがあります。
NCI Preferred Term-J
RR間隔単一測定

xxTEST
RS Wave Amplitude, Aggregate
CDISC Synonym(s)
RS Wave Amplitude, Aggregate
CDISC Definition
An aggregate RS wave amplitude value based on measurements from multiple beats from a single ECG. The method of aggregation, which can vary, is typically a measure of central tendency such as the mean.
NCI Preferred Term
RS Wave Amplitude Aggregate
xxTEST-J
RS波振幅、集計
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
RS波振幅、集計
CDISC Definition-J

NCI Preferred Term-J
RS波振幅総計

CDISC Definition

A relative measurement (ratio or percentage) of a sub-population of helper 17.1 T-lymphocytes to total helper 17.1 T-lymphocytes in a biological specimen.
NCI Preferred Term
Helper 17.1 T-Lymphocyte Subpopulation to Helper 17.1 T-Lymphocyte Ratio Measurement
xxTEST-J
TLym ヘルプ 17.1 サブ/TLymH17.1
CDISC Synonym(s)-J
Tリンパ球ヘルパー 17.1 サブポピュレーション/Tリンパ球ヘルパー 17.1; TLym ヘルプ 17.1 サブ/TLymH17.1
CDISC Definition-J
生物学的標本中のヘルパー 17.1 T リンパ球の総数に対するヘルパー 17.1 T リンパ球のサブ集団の相対的な測定値 (比率またはパーセンテージ)。
NCI Preferred Term-J
ヘルパー17.1 Tリンパ球サブポピュレーションとヘルパー17.1 Tリンパ球比の測定
